etpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":36130,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/05\/11\/laylat-al-qadr-last-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":19570,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Seek Laylat al-Qadr on last night of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 11, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Mu\u2019awiyah ibn Abi Sufyan reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSeek the Night of Decree on the last night of Ramadan.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Ibn Khuzaymah 2189 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0645\u064f\u0639\u064e\u0627\u0648\u0650\u064a\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0633\u064f\u0641\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0627\u0646 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647 \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":4389,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/08\/08\/laylat-al-qadar-seven-nights\/","url_meta":{"origin":19570,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadr in last seven nights of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"August 8, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Umar reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLook for the Night of Decree in the last ten nights of Ramadan. If one of you is weak or unable, then do not be overcome by the remaining seven nights.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1165 Grade:\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":14956,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/14\/last-ten-nights-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":19570,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadr in last ten nights of Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 14, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSearch for the Night of Decree in the odd nights among the last ten nights of Ramadan.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 2017, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 1169 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0627\u0626\u0650\u0634\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20755,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/07\/12\/laylat-al-qadr-dua-ramadan\/","url_meta":{"origin":19570,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Laylat al-Qadr: Dua on Night of Decree in Ramadan","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 12, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, if I know which night is the Night of Decree, what should I say during it?\u201d The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cSay: O Allah, You are pardoning. You love to forgive, so forgive me.\u201d Source: Sunan\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34153,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/04\/30\/laylat-al-qadar-thousand-months\/","url_meta":{"origin":19570,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Laylat al-Qadar better than a thousand months","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 30, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said when the month of Ramadan began, \u201cVerily, this month has presented itself to you. There is a night within it that is better than a thousand months. Whoever is deprived of it has been deprived\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":15513,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/07\/29\/ramadan-knowledge-night-decree\/","url_meta":{"origin":19570,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Ramadan: Knowledge of Laylat al-Qadr removed by insults","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"July 29, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"'Ubadah ibn al-Samit reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, came out to inform people about the Night of Decree\u00a0in Ramadan, but two Muslim men were insulting each other. The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, I have come out to tell you about the Night of Decree, but\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u06